Thos who do escape to the safety of their surface homes return changed. Their eyes have seen the shadows and the gloom, the inevitable doom of the Underdark.&quot;<br>
-- R.A. Salvatore (part of the prelude in the Dark Elf Trilogy)<br>
<br>
She paced from window to table, waiting ever waiting it seemed. Her gaze came to rest upon the dully lit courtyard below. No, this was not Neriak. The city of the dark elves. This was Katta Castellium. Their second home. <br>
They had worked hard to gain favor with the denizens of this twilight city. Had been finally granted a room in the home of Nathym Illuminious. It was here that they had begun to put together their plans for the invasion of Qeynos. <br>
She imagined it would take those summoned days to reach them. Some would need to enter the city under the cloak of stealth. While others would be able to boldly walk the streets. <br>
A soft chuckle from the hearth drew her impatient attention. &quot;They will come Ma Vei.&quot; Nos comforted her from his seat near the fire. A book was open in his lap. He had been studying it for some time though as yet had not shared what he learned from the old tome. It was not in Kat to pry.<br>
Her hands went to absently massage the dull ache in the small of her back as her gaze returned to the courtyard. Her mind reeling with so many things. The potential fall of the city she had long despised. The coming birth of their child. Their past and future collided. &quot;Aye,&quot; she whispered softly in reply, &quot;They will come.. &quot; She missed it, their home, Neriak. She missed the darkness, the shadows... the hatred.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#464446><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unuthilyantalvaros.showPublicProfile?language=EN>NuthilyanTalvaros</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/5/02 9:56:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=557.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://212.212.159.240/wolf/imagesP/wolfh.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Qeynos Burning</span><hr size=1> Nuthilyan walked stealthily down the halls of Katta Castellum, well camoflaged and invisible to the untrained eye. He had been keeping a close watch on his aquaintances within the Violent Harvest, being welcome in most cities on Norrath this was not a very difficult thing for him to do. Luclin however, such a strange place it was. He turned a corner and walked directly into the path of a patrolling guard, quickly ducking to one side and pressing himself up against the nearest wall he held his breath till he was sure the guard had passed out of sight before moving again. As he was about to start creeping down the terraced walkway once more he heard a familiar voice. Concentrating on it he pressed his ear to the rough stone blocks that made up the imposing walls of Katta. Listening carfully he identified the two speakers as Tier`Dal, being fluent in their tongue, and heard of their plans to launch an assault on Qeynos. &quot;What of it?&quot; he mumbled to himself &quot;I have no love for the dimwitted humans who live past the plains of the Karanas, and yet i do see an oppertunity to make something profitable out of this.....&quot; lost in his own thoughts he quickly turned away from the walls and ran off silently into the darkness, heading towards the twilight sea. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.showPrevMessage?topicID=557.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.showNextMessage?topicID=557.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=557.topic&index=2><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~eqmaximus/brell/addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.threadControl?topicID=557.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=557.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisroleplaying.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=557.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="brellserilisfrm70">News and Events<option value="brellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion">The